ors) or too long (wastes user time). Minimum floors of 250ms (bins) and 30ms (sequences) guard against extremely fast hardware."}, {"id": "concept_inline_iife_extendscript", "label": "Inline IIFE ExtendScript pattern (never call named hostscript.jsx functions)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "cep-extension/ext.js", "source_location": "line 155", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Named hostscript.jsx functions silently fail in CEP when called via evalScript. All ExtendScript code in ext.js is therefore inlined as IIFEs to guarantee execution. Fixed in v1.8.3."}], "edges": [{"source": "cep_ext_connectwebsocket", "target": "cep_ext_startprojecttracking", "relation": "calls", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "cep-extension/ext.js", "source_location": "line 98", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "cep_ext_connectwebsocket", "target": "cep_ext_finalizeimportbatch", "relation": "calls", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "cep-extension/ext.js", "source_location": "line 212", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "cep_ext_connectwebsocket", "target": "cep_ext_setupfrompremiertree", "relation": "calls", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "cep-extension/ext.js", "source_location": "line 264", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "cep_ext_connectwebsocket", "target": "cep_ext_setupprojectbinsandsequences", "relation": "calls", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "cep-extension/ext.js", "source_location": "line 266", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "cep_ext_finalizeimportbatch", "target": "cep_csinterface", "relation": "calls", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "cep-extension/ext.js", "source_location": "line 70", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "cep_ext_startprojecttracking", "target": "cep_csinterface", "relation": "calls", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file